entries.femaleVariant: This all you got? Pretty limited selection, if you ask me...
Well, how about number thirty-four? It's our dish-of-the-day this week.
Dish-of-the-day? Ew, I'll pass. Prolly leftovers from last week thrown into a pot.
OK... how about number twenty-eight? It's a favorite with our regulars. Comes with sesame sauce.
OK, sir, well maybe the  chef can make you something special?
A completely new, one-of-a-kind, signature dish.
